title: Superman 23.1 (Bizarro 01) (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
I adjusted the resolution and compression of the original scan for easier reading on tablets and to save space. All credit goes to the original scanner for their hard work. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.


Superman 23.1 (Bizarro 1)

By:   	Sholly Fisch, Jeff Johnson, Aaron Kuder	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Superhero
Publisher:   	DC Comics	
Pub. Date:  	September 04, 2013
Format:         CBZ

Lex Luthors' sinister plan to manipulate Superman's genetic material to create a mindless soldier under his control results in the monster known as Bizarro: opposite of Superman in every way, with no compassion, no remorse and no mercy!
